Adds person **personId** as a member of site **siteId**.

You can set the **role** to one of four types:

* SiteConsumer
* SiteCollaborator
* SiteContributor
* SiteManager

**Note:** You can add more than one site member by 
specifying a list of people in the JSON body like this:

```JSON
[
  {
    "role": "SiteConsumer",
    "id": "joe"
  },
  {
    "role": "SiteConsumer",
    "id": "fred"
  }
]
```
